    "title": "Uwezeshaji wa Roho",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "uwezeshaji wa roho",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Katika Biblia, inapohitajika, Mungu huwapa uwezo maalum wale waliojitolea kumtumikia. Hadithi ya Mose na wazee sabini ni mfano wa awali. Inaonyesha kwamba Mungu ametenda kwa njia maalum miongoni mwa watu wake katika historia yote. Wakati Mose alipokosa uvumilivu kwa Waisraeli waasi, Mungu alimwagiza achague wanaume sabini kumsaidia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:1-Num11:15\">Hesabu 11:1–15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:16-Num11:17\">16–17</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:14-Exod18:26\">Kutoka 18:14–26</a>). Kisha, Mungu alishiriki Roho Mtakatifu aliyekuwa na Mose na wanaume hawa, akiwapa nguvu kwa ajili ya huduma (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:24-Num11:25\">Hesabu 11:24–25</a>).</p><p>Roho wa Mungu alimpa Yoshua nguvu ya ili amrithi baada ya Mose (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:18\">Hesabu 27:18</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:9\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 34:9</a>). Wakati wa Waamuzi, Roho wa Mungu aliwasaidia viongozi wa Israeli. Hii ilijumuisha:</p><ul><li><p>Othnieli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">Waamuzi 3:10</a>);</p></li><li><p>Gideoni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:34\">Waamuzi 6:34</a>);</p></li><li><p>Yeftha (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:29\">Waamuzi 11:29</a>); na</p></li><li><p>Samsoni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:25\">Waamuzi 13:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:6\">14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:19\">19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:14\">15:14</a>).</p></li></ul><p>Mfalme Daudi alipata nguvu kutokana na uwepo wa Mungu. Uelewa wake wa matendo ya Mungu katika historia na maisha yake ulimfanya kuwa kiongozi bora (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:13\">1 Samweli 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:45\">17:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:12\">18:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:28\">28</a>). Manabii walitambua kuwa kazi yao maalum ilikuwa inawezekana kwa sababu ya uwepo na nguvu za Roho (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">Isaya 61:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:5\">Ezekieli 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:6\">Zekaria 4:6</a>).</p><p>Roho wa Mungu alimtia mafuta Yesu na kumpa nguvu kwa ajili ya utume maalum (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:18\">Mathayo 12:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1\">Luka 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:14\">14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:34\">Yohana 3:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">Matendo 10:38</a>). Alizungumza kuhusu jukumu muhimu la Roho katika kanisa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">Matendo 1:8</a>). Kuwasili kwa Roho kuliruhusu Wakristo waliokusanyika kuzungumza kwa ujasiri siku ya Pentekoste (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:4-Acts2:5\">Matendo 2:4–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:16-Acts2:18\">16–18</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:29\">Yoeli 2:28–29</a>).</p><p>Baada ya Pentekoste, Roho aliipa kanisa ujasiri na nguvu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">Matendo 4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:6\">19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:28\">20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:1-1Cor12:31\">1 Wakorintho 12:1–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:2-Gal3:5\">Wagalatia 3:2–5</a>). Roho Mtakatifu bado yupo na watu wa Mungu leo. Roho anafanya kazi inapohitajika ili kuwafufua na kuimarisha watu wa Mungu. Anaendelea kuwaandaa kwa kazi ambazo Mungu anawaita kuzifanya.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:16-Num11:30\">Hesabu 11:16–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:1-Num24:9\">24:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:18-Num27:23\">27:18–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:10-Deut34:12\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 34:10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:9-Judg3:10\">Waamuzi 3:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:34\">6:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:29\">11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:5-Judg14:6\">14:5–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:19\">19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:14\">15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:13\">1 Samweli 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1-Ps23:6\">Zaburi 23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1\">46:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:16-Ps94:19\">94:16–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:1-Ps116:9\">116:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:1-Ps121:8\">121:1–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:10-Ps143:12\">143:10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">Isaya 61:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:5\">Ezekieli 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:29\">Yoeli 2:28–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:6\">Zekaria 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:18\">Mathayo 12:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1\">Luka 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:14\">14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:34\">Yohana 3:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">Matendo 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:4\">2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:16-Acts2:18\">16–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:6\">19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:28\">20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:1-1Cor12:31\">1 Wakorintho 12:1–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:2-Gal3:5\">Wagalatia 3:2–5</a></p>",
